{"tid":16870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇永康陳年舊照","createTime":"2016-12-01T15:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T16:20:25.000Z","uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e420b96b89f73c5f7c20d1101223a0d5287e5142","tid":16870,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"絶不可做分裂國家的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/232245_5cd28adf719b2786cb31212744dfbdcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F232245_5cd28adf719b2786cb31212744dfbdcb.jpg&h=8f8e313f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"700baee5e1832e5327919bf5d8129bf812743735","tid":16870,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0daed0f767a2946df2aed70cce08f7eeec5bce7","tid":16870,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"媽呀好柒呀"},{"pid":"05db5f687fdc752eb90859c462f348a5ae3e5244","tid":16870,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c55a712803070578886680123470f46491c61535","tid":16870,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"咩場合？"},{"pid":"f23b01c4ea5d2194b9bbb76eb88419b19cc1858b","tid":16870,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩場合？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本報訊】正在台灣土城台北看守所接受強迫戒毒的本港歌手蘇永康，在副總統呂秀蓮精心幕後策劃下，昨日在看守所內舉行他至今為止最難忘的「演唱會」，呂秀蓮替他載歌載舞伴唱，蘇永康落力演出之餘，更獲呂秀蓮邀請擔任台灣反毒大使。不過，台灣的網民就批評呂秀蓮安排這次演唱會是在爭取個人曝光，以及要讓蘇永康早日獲釋。而熟悉兩岸政情的分析家就認為，蘇永康與台獨急先鋒的呂秀蓮共舞是吉凶未卜，有可能會觸怒北京，重蹈昔日台灣歌后張惠妹被封殺的覆轍。"},{"pid":"3abe7edbb222bfd96f93f60ebd89e067a37cc722","tid":16870,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bfaae681f443fa3b24d4843fab7ce03384079d","tid":16870,"uid":43597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到咁盡  乜都原諒佢啦"}]}